{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ABOUT THIS GAME</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Utter Takedown</strong> is a gripping top-down tactical hard-core stealth game set in the 2000s. You play as a former hitman who has left the local mafia, only to have his family threatened as retaliation. Now, it's up to you to take down the mafia and save your loved ones. With a variety of interactive tools and weapons at your disposal - from knifes and tasers to cameras and toggles - you'll need to use all of your wits and strategic thinking to succeed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game features a diverse range of maps, each with its own unique challenges and obstacles to overcome. As you progress, you'll encounter different types of AI with varying levels of difficulty, adding an extra layer of complexity to the gameplay. Along the way, you'll need to solve puzzles, gather intel, and outsmart your enemies to stay one step ahead.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Utter Takedown offers a thrilling and immersive gaming experience. With its combination of action, strategy, and puzzle-solving, it's the perfect game for anyone who loves a challenge. So gear up, get ready, and prepare to make an utter mafia takedown.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"That's my job!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2338500/a074c2ca6a9cc62a292bfab53ba787644da7231b.jpg"},{"name":"What's the secret?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2338500/74fb6c6b400d581bf8269e1396c3a90762f7c6bc.jpg"},{"name":"Dude","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2338500/d401970d3c850a884de2059e87fc18063e2e9147.jpg"},{"name":"Perfectly done!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2338500/0ade02492be4af5d854a6dbf9769ab96450488aa.jpg"},{"name":"How did you do th